namespace Pizza

features
	Pizza {abstract}	
		mandatory
			Topping	
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella {abstract}
			Size	
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough	
				alternative
					Neapolitan {abstract}
					Sicilian

		optional
			CheesyCrust

constraints
	CheesyCrust => !Big
	Big => !Ham
	Sicilian => !Mozzarella
	Mozzarella => !Salami
	Salami => !Big